quran[11{c,v,t}:
21,91,Wallateee ahsanat farjahaa fanafakhnaa feehaa mir roohinaa wa ja'alnaahaa wabnahaaa Aayatal lil'aalameen
21,92,Inna haaziheee ummatukum ummatanw waahidatanw wa Ana Rabbukum fa'budoon
21,93,Wa taqatta'ooo amrahum bainahum kullun ilainaaa raaji'oon (section 6)
21,94,Famai ya'mal minas saalihaati wa huwa mu'minun falaa kufraana lisa'yihee wa innaa lahoo kaatiboon
21,95,Wa haraamun 'alaa qaryatin ahlaknaahaaa annahum laa yarji'oon
21,96,Hattaaa izaa futihat Yaajooju wa Maajooju wa hum min kulli hadabiny yansiloon
21,97,Waqtarabal wa'dul haqqu fa-izaa hiya shaakhisatun absaarul lazeena kafaroo yaawailanaa qad kunna fee ghaflatim min haaza bal kunnaa zaalimeen
21,98,Innakum wa maa ta'budoona min doonil laahi hasabu Jahannama antum lahaa waaridoon
21,99,Law kaana haaa'ulaaa'i aalihatam maa waradoohaa wa kullun feehaa khaalidoon
21,100,Lahum feehaa zafeerunw wa hum feehaa laa yasma'oon
21,101,Innal lazeena sabaqat lahum minnal husnaaa ulaaa'ika 'anhaa mub'adoon
